    "featureType": "projectfu.supportModule",
    "data": {
      "description": "<p>After a creature aboard this <strong>personal vehicle</strong> is hit by a <strong>ranged</strong> attack, if you are driving this <strong>vehicle</strong>, you may spend 1 Inventory Point. If you do, the attacker suffers 10 <strong>physical</strong> damage (after their attack has been resolved). This amount increases by 5 damage if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 10 damage if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>.</p><hr /><p><strong>You Spend:</strong> @LOSS[1 ip]<br /><strong>Target Suffers: </strong>@DMG[&amp;step(10,15,20) physical]{Physical Damage}</p>",
      "complex": false
    },
    "source": "FUTF168",
    "fuid": "counterstrike-module"
  },
